zeq-8", "name": "Recon Drone", "equipped": false, "quantity": 1}, {"id": "zeq-9", "name": "Chromatophore Backpack", "equipped": false, "quantity": 1}, {"id": "zeq-10", "name": "12mm Handgun", "equipped": false, "quantity": 1}, {"id": "zeq-11", "name": "Urban Ranger 10mm Handgun", "equipped": false, "quantity": 1}, {"id": "zeq-12", "name": "Biometric Pass", "equipped": false, "quantity": 1}, {"id": "zeq-13", "name": "Nanodoc", "equipped": false, "quantity": 10}, {"id": "zeq-14", "name": "Collapsible Ladder", "equipped": false, "quantity": 2}, {"id": "zeq-15", "name": "Jammer", "equipped": false, "quantity": 1}]	{"satoshi": 18355}	[{"id":"zf-1","name":"Aquatic","source":"Genetic","description":"You are adapted to a marine environment with webbed digits and functional gills. You gain a Swim speed of 6 metres and can breathe underwater. When you surface, the lungful of water is expelled through the mouth."},{"id":"zf-2","name":"Ambidexterity","source":"Genetic","description":"You are equally dextrous with both hands. You can make off-hand attacks without the penalty normally imposed for doing so, and you do not suffer disadvantage on any check or attack roll due to using your non-dominant hand."},{"id":"zf-3","name":"Photosynthesis","source":"Genetic","description":"Your skin contains chlorophyll-producing cells that let you absorb solar energy. If you spend at least 4 hours per day in direct sunlight, your food and water requirements are halved. During a short rest taken in direct sunlight, you may roll one additional Hit Die when spending Hit Dice to recover hit points."},{"id":"zf-4","name":"Swift","source":"Genetic","description":"Your base walking speed increases by 3 metres (10 ft)."},{"id":"zf-5","name":"Acute Senses","source":"Genetic","description":"You gain proficiency in Perception (expertise if already proficient) and can see in dim light within 18 metres as if it were bright light, and in darkness as if it were dim light."},{"id":"zf-6","name":"Enhanced Dexterity","source":"Genetic","description":"Your Dexterity score increases by 2, to a maximum of 20."},{"id":"zf-7","name":"Quills","source":"Genetic","description":"Retractable quills cover parts of your body. As a reaction when a creature grapples you or hits you with a melee attack, you may deal 1d4 piercing damage to the attacker. You may also launch quills as a ranged attack (range 6 m / 18 m), dealing 1d4 piercing damage."},{"id":"zf-8","name":"Enhanced Wisdom","source":"Genetic","description":"Your Wisdom score increases by 2, to a maximum of 20."},{"id":"zf-9","name":"Horticulturist (+2)","source":"Vocation","description":"Your specialist training in plant science grants a +2 bonus on Intelligence checks related to plants, cultivation, and botany. You can identify any plant on a DC 10 Intelligence (Horticulturist) check and immediately know its basic properties, toxicity, and uses. You also gain double proficiency on Horticulturist vocational checks."},{"id":"zf-10","name":"Seasoned","source":"Aptitude","description":"Years of field experience have sharpened your instincts. You gain proficiency in one additional skill or tool of your choice, and when you make an ability check in your primary area of expertise you may treat a roll of 9 or lower on the d20 as a 10."},{"id":"zf-11","name":"Leviathan Friendo","source":"Environmental","description":"Through repeated respectful encounters you have earned the trust of Leviathan transgenics. Leviathans will not attack you without significant provocation and will extend you a degree of professional courtesy. You gain advantage on Charisma checks when interacting with Leviathans."},{"id":"zf-12","name":"Cyberoptics","source":"Cybernetic","description":"Your natural eyes have been replaced with cybernetic ocular implants. You treat dim light as bright light, you gain a +2 bonus on Perception checks that rely on sight, and you can interface with digital networks for augmented-reality displays and data overlays."},{"id":"zf-13","name":"Electric Organ","source":"Bioware","description":"The target takes 10d6 electrical damage on a failed Dexterity save (DC = 16), or half as much on a successful one."}]	[]	[]	[]	0	16	2026-03-16 04:01:28.284157	2026-03-16 04:01:28.284157		18355	0	{"spectrum": false, "darkvision": true, "macrovision": true, "microvision": true, "penetration": false, "acuteOlfaction": false}	\N	\N	\N
