(Insight) checks; suffer 1 level of exhaustion afterward.","launchTime":"1 action"},{"id":"zero-hack-postmortem","name":"Post Mortem","type":"Injection","level":1,"effect":"Inject dead body (less than 48 hours, no massive head trauma); hack its daemon/memories to answer questions. One use only per corpse.","launchTime":"1 action"},{"id":"zero-hack-angel","name":"Angel","type":"Injection","level":1,"effect":"Regain 2 hp every turn (stabilizes dying); used by medics. 1 level of exhaustion after.","launchTime":"1 action"},{"id":"zero-hack-blooddope","name":"Blood Dope","type":"Injection","level":1,"effect":"Target gains 1d10+5 temporary hit points for the duration.","launchTime":"1 action"},{"id":"zero-hack-buddha","name":"Buddha","type":"Injection","level":1,"effect":"Target gains +2 Wis and Cha; must make DC 10 Wis save to take any violent action. Melee hack attack required if unwilling.","launchTime":"1 action"},{"id":"zero-hack-chromato","name":"Chromatophores","type":"Injection","level":1,"effect":"Target's skin mimics chromatophore camouflage; target is invisible. Must be unclothed or wearing transparent clothing.","launchTime":"1 minute"},{"id":"zero-hack-shark","name":"Shark","type":"Injection","level":1,"effect":"Drug heightens empathy; target gains +2 Charisma for 30 minutes.","launchTime":"1 action"},{"id":"zero-hack-superman","name":"Superman","type":"Injection","level":1,"effect":"Stimulants drown pain; if reduced to 0 HP and don't die outright, make DC 10 Con save to drop to 1 HP instead. DC increases by 5 each subsequent use.","launchTime":"1 action"},{"id":"zero-hack-claws","name":"Claws","type":"Gadget","level":1,"effect":"Nanocarbon claws on fingertips; light finesse simple melee weapon that deals 2d4 AP slashing damage. Falls off when hack ends.","launchTime":"1 minute"},{"id":"zero-hack-toxicjet","name":"Toxic Jet","type":"Gadget","level":1,"effect":"Air-jet device fires toxic gas at a creature within 3m; Con save or take 3d12 poison damage.","launchTime":"1 action"},{"id":"zero-hack-geckoskin","name":"Gecko Skin","type":"Gadget","level":1,"effect":"Biobots coat hands, feet, legs, and arms to mimic gecko skin; climb walls and ceilings with hands free. Climbing speed equals walking speed.","launchTime":"1 minute"},{"id":"zero-hack-forensicscan","name":"Forensic Scan","type":"Gadget","level":1,"effect":"Analyze chemical and biological composition of up to a cubic meter. Can sequence individual DNA samples and identify persons via government databases.","launchTime":"1 minute"},{"id":"zero-hack-enhance","name":"Enhance Ability","type":"Injection","level":1,"effect":"Choose one ability type: advantage on those checks, plus bonus (Endurance: +2d6 temp HP; Strength: double carry; Dexterity: no fall <6m if not incapacitated).","launchTime":"1 action"},{"id":"zero-hack-enamoringcloud","name":"Enamoring Cloud","type":"Gadget","level":2,"effect":"Release bioactive nanobots; living creatures within 18m without independent air supply make Wis save or become charmed by you.","launchTime":"1 action"}]	dexterity	14	6	{"1":{"used":2,"total":7},"2":{"used":1,"total":2}}	[{"id":"zeq-1","name":"Nanofiber Vest","equipped":true,"quantity":1},{"id":"zeq-2","name":"Biohacking Kit","equipped":false,"quantity":18},{"id":"zeq-3","name":"Gadget Hacking Kit","equipped":false,"quantity":18},{"id":"zeq-4","name":"Stun Baton Charges","equipped":false,"quantity":3},{"id":"zeq-5","name":"9mm Handgun","equipped":false,"quantity":3},{"id":"zeq-6","name":"SMG 4.9mm","equipped":false,"quantity":1},{"id":"zeq-7","name":"Overclock Hex","equipped":false,"quantity":1},{"id":"zeq-8","name":"Recon Drone","equipped":false,"quantity":1},{"id":"zeq-9","name":"Chromatophore Backpack","equipped":false,"quantity":1},{"id":"zeq-10","name":"12mm Handgun","equipped":false,"quantity":1},{"id":"zeq-11","name":"Urban Ranger 10mm Handgun","equipped":false,"quantity":1},{"id":"zeq-12","name":"Biometric Pass","equipped":false,"quantity":1},{"id":"zeq-13","name":"Nanodoc","equipped":false,"quantity":10},{"id":"zeq-14","name":"Collapsible Ladder","equipped":false,"quantity":2},{"id":"zeq-15","name":"Jammer","equipped":false,"quantity":1}]	{"satoshi":18355}	[{"id":"zf-1","name":"Aquatic","source":"Genetic","description":"You are adapted to a marine environment with webbed digits and functional gills. You gain a Swim speed of 6 metres and can breathe underwater. When you surface, the lungful of water is expelled through the mouth."},{"id":"zf-2","name":"Ambidexterity","source":"Genetic","description":"You are equally dextrous with both hands. You can make off-hand attacks without the penalty normally imposed for doing so, and you do not suffer disadvantage on any check or attack roll due to using your non-dominant hand."},{"id":"zf-3","name":"Photosynthesis","source":"Genetic","description":"Your skin contains chlorophyll-producing cells that let you absorb solar energy. If you spend at least 4 hours per day in direct sunlight, your food and water requirements are halved. During a short rest taken in direct sunlight, you may roll one additional Hit Die when spending Hit Dice to recover hit points."},{"id":"zf-4","name":"Swift","source":"Genetic","description":"Your base walking speed increases by 3 metres (10 ft)."},{"id":"zf-5","name":"Acute Senses","source":"Genetic","description":"You gain proficiency in Perception (expertise if already proficient) and can see in dim light within 18 metres as if it were bright light, and in darkness as if it were dim light."},{"id":"zf-6","name":"Enhanced Dexterity","source":"Genetic","description":"Your Dexterity score increases by 2, to a maximum of 20."},{"id":"zf-7","name":"Quills","source":"Genetic","description":"Retractable quills cover parts of your body. As a reaction when a creature grapples you or hits you with a melee attack, you may deal 1d4 piercing damage to the attacker. You may also launch quills as a ranged attack (range 6 m / 18 m), dealing 1d4 piercing damage."},{"id":"zf-8","name":"Enhanced Wisdom","source":"Genetic","description":"Your Wisdom score increases by 2, to a maximum of 20."},{"id":"zf-9","name":"Horticulturist (+2)","source":"Vocation","description":"Your specialist training in plant science grants a +2 bonus on Intelligence checks related to plants, cultivation, and botany. You can identify any plant on a DC 10 Intelligence (Horticulturist) check and immediately know its basic properties, toxicity, and uses. You also gain double proficiency on Horticulturist vocational checks."},{"id":"zf-10","name":"Seasoned","source":"Aptitude","description":"Years of field experience have sharpened your instincts. You gain proficiency in one additional skill or tool of your choice, and when you make an ability check in your primary area of expertise you may treat a roll of 9 or lower on the d20 as a 10."},{"id":"zf-11","name":"Leviathan Friendo","source":"Environmental","description":"Through repeated respectful encounters you have earned the trust of Leviathan transgenics. Leviathans will not attack you without significant provocation and will extend you a degree of professional courtesy. You gain advantage on Charisma checks when interacting with Leviathans."},{"id":"zf-12","name":"Cyberoptics","source":"Cybernetic","description":"Your natural eyes have been replaced with cybernetic ocular implants. You treat dim light as bright light, you gain a +2 bonus on Perception checks that rely on sight, and you can interface with digital networks for augmented-reality displays and data overlays."},{"id":"zf-13","name":"Electric Organ","source":"Bioware","description":"The target takes 10d6 electrical damage on a failed Dexterity save (DC = 16), or half as much on a successful one."}]	[]	[]	[]	0	16	2026-03-16 06:09:05.480057	2026-03-16 06:09:05.480057		18355	0	{"spectrum":false,"darkvision":true,"macrovision":true,"microvision":true,"penetration":false,"acuteOlfaction":false}	\N	2026-03-16 06:09:05.479	\N
