ng cells and tissues, creating biological constructs and healing allies at the cellular level."},{"name":"Dr. Frankenstein","description":"Dr. Frankensteins push the boundaries of biological modification, creating monstrous augmentations and chimeric organisms."},{"name":"Protean Grinder","description":"Protean Grinders focus on self-modification, constantly adapting their own biology to meet any challenge."}]
