a."},{"name":"Puppeteer","description":"Puppeteers manipulate drones, robots, and electronic devices, turning the battlefield's technology against their enemies."},{"name":"Synergist","description":"Synergists enhance their allies' capabilities through digital buffs and network coordination."}]
